## 🚀 사용 예제

### 1. 안정성 테스트
```javascript
import { StabilityTestRunner } from './stability-tester.js';

const runner = new StabilityTestRunner(48);  // 48시간
const result = runner.runTest(1000);

console.log(`Success rate: ${result.successRate}`);
console.log(`Memory leak: ${result.memoryLeak.leak ? 'YES' : 'NO'}`);

const report = runner.generateReport();
console.log(`Overall status: ${report.overallStatus}`);
```

### 2. Chaos Engineering
```javascript
import { ChaosTestRunner } from './chaos-engineer.js';

const chaos = new ChaosTestRunner();

// 시나리오 추가
chaos.addScenario('High Latency', 'latency', 'api-service', 5000);
chaos.addScenario('High Error Rate', 'error', 'database', 3000);

// 실행
const results = chaos.runAllScenarios();
const report = chaos.generateReport();

console.log(`Scenarios executed: ${report.executedScenarios}`);
console.log(`Resilience pass rate: ${report.resilience.passRate}`);
```

### 3. 보안 감사
```javascript
import { SecurityAuditRunner } from './security-auditor.js';

const auditor = new SecurityAuditRunner();
const auditResult = auditor.runAudit();

console.log(`Security score: ${auditResult.score.score}/100`);
console.log(`Grade: ${auditResult.score.grade}`);
console.log(`Status: ${auditResult.status}`);
```

### 4. 성능 벤치마크
```javascript
import { BenchmarkRunner } from './performance-benchmarker.js';

const runner = new BenchmarkRunner();
const report = runner.generateReport();

console.log(`Throughput: ${report.throughput.results[0].throughput}`);
console.log(`Latency P95: ${report.latency.measurements[0].p95}`);
console.log(`Memory change: ${report.memory.snapshots[1]}`);
```

